[node name="PuzzleDescription" type="Label" parent="."]
offset_left = -680.0
offset_top = -573.0
offset_right = 33.0
offset_bottom = -290.0
text = "Requires knowledge of 6 recipes in order to complete:
Strength Potion from merchant, traded for green 
herb grinds, which a book is found on the ground.
Strength potion requires:
Yellow Dust, which is part of merchant's book.
Red Berry Seed, which is learned from a hint on the wall,
Saturated Stem, which is part of merchant's book. Crafting requires knowledge of:
Gray Juice, Obtained by description from NPC
and knowledge on how to cut flowers.

order: Herb Grinds -> Str book + Red Seed + Juice -> Craft Str Pot -> move boulder -> win"

